{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"c903b2810d","title":"谢富治戚本禹接见红卫医院两派组织的讲话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"ba45fd5473","index":0,"year":1967,"month":10,"day":21,"articleId":"c903b2810d","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"李震","id":"155c01ead4","type":"人物"},{"name":"刘少奇","id":"3aaab89c2a","type":"人物"},{"name":"戚本禹","id":"57434e107b","type":"人物"},{"name":"江青","id":"82305e518c","type":"人物"},{"name":"谢富治","id":"93cca4665d","type":"人物"},{"name":"医药卫生","id":"b55010d172","type":"主题"},{"name":"关键人物文稿","id":"c20d333791","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"发言","id":"e23dcf99fa","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"85b13f5c0b","name":"谢富治"},{"id":"9014e20fdf","name":"戚本禹"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"13eef09afd","type":"title","text":"谢富治戚本禹接见红卫医院两派组织的讲话","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c903b2810d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4367121c31","type":"paragraph","text":"〖时间：3：25至3：55，地点：人大会堂。红卫医院即安定医院。清华井冈山、北医八一八、地院东方红、医大红旗、公安部×局、学部等同志出席。〗","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c903b2810d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"bb750c7760","type":"paragraph","text":"戚本禹同志讲：今天找大家谈谈陈里宁问题，我们作了很多调查，请谢富治同志谈谈。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c903b2810d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e1b04ac880","type":"paragraph","text":"谢副总理：陈里宁的事我没有好好管，戚本禹管了（戚本禹同志说：开始管了一段）公安部李震管。听说为了陈里宁的事你们医院涉及到你们学校（戚本禹同志：医务界）医务界有很大争论，有的说是响当当的左派，有的说是反革命，攻击伟大领袖，我们过去没好好研究，最近作了些调查，群众组织也作了调查，今天与同志们商量一下，不要因为这么一个人的事情妨碍大联合，我们可以把这个问题搞清楚。争起来没什么意思，可不可以这样肯定，这个人当时写了相当多的材料反对刘少奇，反对中国的赫鲁晓夫，反对刘少奇这件事是对的，不能因反刘少奇把这个人就怎么样，不要把反对刘少奇这点作为这个人犯罪的罪名，因为全党全国都在批判刘少奇。但是这个人同时也有很大错误，对我们伟大领袖毛主席光辉著作，作了大量的修改错误的批判、攻击（戚本禹同志说：是歪曲）甚至是攻击、歪曲，这是很大的错误（戚本禹同志说：反动的）反动的，这部分分量是少，研究这些东西是很困难的，混乱（李震：逻辑混乱）不管怎么样是错误的。但是从全部过程看，这个人神经不健康，我们没有学过医。你们在坐的有好多学过医，这个人起码在某些时候神经不清，所以他的东西，就不能作正确的判断，因此不能说他是什么响当当的左派，因为他反刘少奇的同时也攻击伟大领袖毛主席，所以不能说是无产阶级革命派。至于这个人有什么其他问题，可以观察，可以了解。有一点可结论，反对刘少奇是没罪的，但攻击伟大领袖毛主席是不准许的，这种人不能成为真正无产阶级革命派，将来有别的问题审查。如果是精神病要治，有什么问题今后审查，所以争论就没意义，肯定精神不太健康。金大夫，我见你几次（金大夫：两次）揭露这个问题，心是好的，愿望是好的，后来有了派性，是不是？金大夫（金大夫：是，是有派性）有了派性就不是实事求是，这是一个经验。","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c903b2810d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"79b5568774","type":"paragraph","text":"今天宣布一下，这个事不要再搞了，这个人交有关单位处理。报告不作了，书不出了，剧不演了（戚本禹：报告五月就停止了）两派不要抓住互相搞。他是精神病，今天是不是达成这个协议，搞提乌烟瘴气，这个人的处理交给我们办，停止争论，停止演剧，停止报告，不能做无产阶级革命派，原来讲这件事情是好心，后来有点派性，不要争论这个问题，把这人交国家机关处理。我讲的清楚吗？","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c903b2810d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cc5b1475d8","type":"paragraph","text":"戚本禹同志讲：很清楚！很清楚！","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c903b2810d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7393b61da1","type":"paragraph","text":"医大红旗高××：我们坚决同意谢副总理指示，现在他们“狂人日记”全国卖的很广，小学他们作教材学，连内蒙古、拉萨也有，在科技东方红翻印的“狂人日记”第一页上写着：江青给毛主席看了，毛主席说好。","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c903b2810d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8c8d55fbdc","type":"paragraph","text":"戚本禹同志：你们把谢副总理的话讲出去，就行了，说江青同志给毛主席看了没有这回事。这是谣言，谁给造出去的。","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c903b2810d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"05ee15913c","type":"paragraph","text":"孙××：红旗战斗队负责人在大会上公布的还有传单。","index":8,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c903b2810d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9558849c89","type":"paragraph","text":"戚本禹同志：没有这回事，谁造出去的。","index":9,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c903b2810d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d26e07362b","type":"paragraph","text":"孙××：是科大东方红。","index":10,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c903b2810d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b6734e523d","type":"paragraph","text":"戚本禹同志：根本不会有这回事，我问了江青同志没这回事。科大东方红是什么组织？","index":11,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c903b2810d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d8ab24f026","type":"paragraph","text":"孙××：科大东方红就是科学技术大学的东方红。","index":12,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c903b2810d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0742c0e384","type":"paragraph","text":"戚本禹同志：现在作正式声明，你们两派不要争论了，好不好。你们把谢副总理讲话公布出去，就行了。","index":13,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c903b2810d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a34102562b","type":"paragraph","text":"医大：双方立即停止对这问题的争论，可以停战，坚决照办。","index":14,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c903b2810d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"71c138a996","type":"paragraph","text":"谢副总理：可以不可以停止争论了？众答：可以。","index":15,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c903b2810d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b34b8a6245","type":"paragraph","text":"戚本禹同志：因为有派性就坚持，你们不要为难他们，主要是你们，他们也不一定是坏心，这个问题你们胜利不等于你们别的都正确，开始陈里宁批判刘少奇是对的。因为十三局光整理了批判刘少奇的材料，这个谢副总理严厉批评过，听说有人当面不说有病，背后说有精神病。","index":16,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c903b2810d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ebf51b3679","type":"paragraph","text":"谢副总理：金大夫你们，有什么意见？","index":17,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c903b2810d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"da8a42b6a2","type":"paragraph","text":"金××：坚决照办。","index":18,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c903b2810d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"66af7373d9","type":"paragraph","text":"王××：我坚决拥护谢副总理的指示，我们当时有许多工作作的不够仔细，有缺点，但大方向正确，目前形势大好。","index":19,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c903b2810d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"495d959913","type":"paragraph","text":"戚本禹同志：他这样检讨，态度是好的。","index":20,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c903b2810d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"897e377ec5","type":"paragraph","text":"王××：（读一段井冈山小报上刊登的最高指示，汇报了清华大联合情况）","index":21,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c903b2810d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a1e8e74e1b","type":"paragraph","text":"谢副总理：要大联合。","index":22,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c903b2810d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d80d4b559f","type":"paragraph","text":"戚本禹同志：“四一四思潮必胜”应彻底批判，你们团派也有缺点，要认清是非，要大联合。","index":23,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c903b2810d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"865770f29a","type":"paragraph","text":"王××：目前阶级斗争很复杂。","index":24,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c903b2810d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"74fe60b010","type":"paragraph","text":"谢副总理：昨天还打架。","index":25,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c903b2810d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f3f1c700ad","type":"paragraph","text":"（王××汇报了清华××问题）","index":26,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c903b2810d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3f8fe3c156","type":"paragraph","text":"戚本禹同志：李××要搞清楚，你们要建立一个专案组，协助公安机关搞。","index":27,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c903b2810d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e889e6d6aa","type":"paragraph","text":"王××：两派冲击利害，容易被坏人利用。","index":28,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c903b2810d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"fa6e2c32a4","type":"paragraph","text":"医大：××还作报告。","index":29,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c903b2810d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d468259a31","type":"paragraph","text":"戚本禹同志：以前大串联可以嘛！既往不咎，分清是非。","index":30,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c903b2810d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6e3bd24383","type":"paragraph","text":"谢副总理：以前大串联是对的（医大：是对的）现在最高指示你们登的很多，有真的也有假的。众：笑。","index":31,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c903b2810d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"bb94b152f5","type":"paragraph","text":"戚本禹同志：（把小报接过去）意思对，但我没有听过。","index":32,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c903b2810d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"21daac2e4a","type":"paragraph","text":"曹××：我们坚决执行谢副总理指示，回去传达！中央作出的正确结论我们坚决拥护！有关材料应上报，全市斗争形势复杂，应提高警惕。十六号全北京市贴出很多大字报……。","index":33,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c903b2810d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"860dc2a625","type":"paragraph","text":"戚本禹同志：听说有的大字报陈里宁名字打×刘少奇却没打……。","index":34,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c903b2810d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e400c98e14","type":"paragraph","text":"金××：学部的大字报有。","index":35,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c903b2810d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5cfa415bc4","type":"paragraph","text":"戚本禹同志：问付××来了没有？有没有？","index":36,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c903b2810d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"44a9767fbc","type":"paragraph","text":"付××：我不了解。","index":37,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c903b2810d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cc9dc26a23","type":"paragraph","text":"谢副总理：千万不要再为这件事搞分歧，争论了。","index":38,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c903b2810d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4d42b297fa","type":"paragraph","text":"医大：“狂人日记”各地都翻印，印的很多，要求让他们都收回来。","index":39,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c903b2810d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7fff562ea8","type":"paragraph","text":"戚本禹同志：让他们自己发表声明，给他们主动权。","index":40,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c903b2810d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0129dfc62d","type":"paragraph","text":"甄××：我们坚决按首长指示办事，发表声明。","index":41,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c903b2810d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8012c67f15","type":"paragraph","text":"戚本禹同志：我们不是首长，谢副总理是首长。","index":42,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c903b2810d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"721dad82ff","type":"paragraph","text":"孙××：戚本禹同志您在为陈里宁平反的时候，提到王福显，这人有病，现在住院……。","index":43,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c903b2810d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a31546526b","type":"paragraph","text":"戚本禹：这事我们不了解。","index":44,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c903b2810d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"34ee5d48eb","type":"paragraph","text":"医大：提到××专案组问题。","index":45,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c903b2810d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"954dd463af","type":"paragraph","text":"戚本禹同志：不要搞了，以后单独找你们谈。今天的会就这样结束吧！","index":46,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c903b2810d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"010d2f1c5a","type":"paragraph","text":"（全体起立，以热烈掌声欢送首长）","index":47,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c903b2810d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"eeff0e1c2b","type":"paragraph","text":"红卫医院红旗战斗队记录整理一九六七年十月廿一日凌晨","index":48,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c903b2810d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8485d54bb2","type":"paragraph","text":"（记录稿未经首长审阅，有错误由整理者负责）  请张贴，请转抄。","index":49,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c903b2810d","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}